'''聶魯達撞擊坑'''（{{lang-en|Neruda}}）是一個位於[[水星|水星]]的隕石坑，直徑約112公里<ref>{{cite book |title = The Data Book of Astronomy |url = https://archive.org/details/databookofastron0000moor |last = Moore |first = Patrick |year = 2000 |publisher = Institute of Physics Publishing |isbn = 0-7503-0620-3}}</ref>。該撞擊坑是由[[國際天文聯會|國際天文聯會]]於2008年以[[智利|智利]]詩人[[巴勃羅·聶魯達|巴勃羅·聶魯達]]命名<ref>{{cite web |url = http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/14931 |title = Neruda |publisher = NASA |work = Gazetteer of Planetary Nomenclature |accessdate = 4 July 2012 |archive-date = 2016-12-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161221204731/https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/14931 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

